# ── Music output directory ─────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Absolute path on your HOST machine that will be mounted into the container.
MUSIC_DIR=/absolute/path/to/your/music/folder

# ── YouTube cookies (optional but recommended) ────────────────────────────
# If you see "Sign in to confirm you're not a bot" errors, export your
# YouTube cookies and mount them into the container.
#
# How to export:
#   1. Install the "Get cookies.txt LOCALLY" extension in Chrome/Firefox
#   2. Go to https://www.youtube.com while logged in
#   3. Click the extension icon and export cookies.txt
#   4. Set COOKIES_PATH to the absolute path of that file:
#
# COOKIES_PATH=/absolute/path/to/cookies.txt
#
# Leave commented out (or empty) to skip — a harmless empty placeholder
# file will be mounted instead.
